WEBVTT

00:00:00.720 --> 00:00:04.080
-EVYAT'SOT DEVYANOSTO SHESTOGO GODA.

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:08.570
Kasriel Koblents. KAUNAS, LITVA.

00:00:14.085 --> 00:00:15.660
undz hot opgeshtelt

00:00:15.660 --> 00:00:17.218
a eltere froy.

00:00:17.460 --> 00:00:20.510
zi hot mit undz geredt oyf litvish. hot zi gezogt,

00:00:20.510 --> 00:00:26.314
"geyt nit itster in Kovne, vayl in Slabodke iz geven a groyser pogrom. m'hot oysgeharget zeyer fil yidn.

00:00:26.455 --> 00:00:28.797
un kumt arayn bay mir in shtub;

00:00:28.797 --> 00:00:31.376
ir vet zikh arumvashn, ir ⟨z-⟩ vet zikh opruen.

00:00:31.568 --> 00:00:33.536
ikh vel aykh onkormenen.

00:00:33.694 --> 00:00:36.780
un az s'vet vern in ovnt fintster,

00:00:36.780 --> 00:00:38.002
dan vet ir

00:00:38.002 --> 00:00:40.488
vi nit iz araynkumen in Kovne."

00:00:40.883 --> 00:00:42.851
azoy iz geven. mir hobn zikh bay ir,

00:00:42.874 --> 00:00:46.732
umgefer a finf, zeks sho hobn mir zikh bay ir, zaynen geven bay ir in shtub.

00:00:47.278 --> 00:00:49.516
zi iz geven a eyntslne froy iz zi geven.

00:00:49.843 --> 00:00:51.136
in ovnt

00:00:51.447 --> 00:00:58.984
bin ikh gekum- zaynen mir gekumen durkhn barg, bin ikh oyf, durkh MACKEVIČIAUS dortn aru- arunter oyf ITALIJOS...

00:00:59.513 --> 00:01:01.498
itster MACKE- dan iz geven ITALIJOS...

00:01:02.888 --> 00:01:06.729
un ikh bin arayn tsu mayn shvester ⟨un bay⟩, ikh hob ongeklapt bay nakht in tir.

00:01:07.714 --> 00:01:09.960
s'iz geven zeyer shpet iz shoyn geven,

00:01:09.960 --> 00:01:14.728
⟨nor, nor m'hot⟩ mir arayngelozn in shtub, hob ikh shoyn gefunen, der bruder iz shoyn geven in shtub.

00:01:14.768 --> 00:01:17.397
dortn... er iz vayter nit gelofn.

00:01:17.397 --> 00:01:20.650
m'hot genumen bashisn fun hoyf, hot er zikh tsurikgekert aheym.

00:01:21.298 --> 00:01:23.890
nu, ikh bin arayn in shtub....

00:01:24.133 --> 00:01:25.510
dos iz bay Tshernen?

00:01:25.146 --> 00:01:26.456
bay Tshernen, ya.

00:01:27.660 --> 00:01:34.455
 nu, ot azoy hot zikh onge- azoy hot zikh geendikt ⟨dem⟩ UNK mayn loyfn fun Kovne.

00:01:35.170 --> 00:01:38.792
vos hot ir geton di ershte teg nokhn kumen, in Kovne?

00:01:38.950 --> 00:01:43.980
di ershte teg nokhn kumen in Kovne iz geven a problem mit produktn; s'iz nit geven vos tsum esn.

00:01:43.980 --> 00:01:46.160
ikh hob oysgezen

00:01:46.160 --> 00:01:50.604
azoy vi a, a blonder; ikh bin in gantsn nit geven pakhozhe oyf keyn...

00:01:49.969 --> 00:01:52.376
nit ⟨keyn,⟩ nit enlekh oyf keyn yidn zayt ir geven.

00:01:51.572 --> 00:01:53.743
in gantsn nit pakhozhe oyf keyn yidn.

00:01:53.160 --> 00:01:54.160
⟨.⟩

00:01:53.766 --> 00:01:55.290
blonde hor hob ikh gehat.

00:01:55.290 --> 00:01:59.750
iz ikh fleg geyn iber di geshef- iber di gesheftn OBESPECHIVen;

00:01:59.750 --> 00:02:01.360
me ⟨s- fleg⟩ gebn, me fleg gebn...

00:02:00.428 --> 00:02:02.248
bazorgn, ya? bazorgn.

00:02:01.360 --> 00:02:05.606
bazorgn mit, mit broyt. v⟨os s'iz⟩ geven d⟨UNK⟩ broyt iz geven.

00:02:06.422 --> 00:02:12.204
ikh bin geven ⟨d-⟩ arayn eyn mol, oyf LAISVĖS aley, dortn iz geven a PARAMA, a gesheft.

00:02:12.565 --> 00:02:14.668
dortn iz geven groyse otsheredn oyf broyt.

00:02:14.387 --> 00:02:15.680
reyen, ye?

00:02:15.585 --> 00:02:17.435
groyse reyen geven, ye.

00:02:17.897 --> 00:02:23.746
groyse reyen oyf broyt. nu, hob ikh zikh geshtelt in rey un ikh hob gevart s'zol tsugeyn mayn rey tsu di...

00:02:22.450 --> 00:02:23.450
rey.

00:02:23.905 --> 00:02:26.936
vi nor ikh bin tsugegangen tsu di farkoyferke,

00:02:28.174 --> 00:02:31.306
hot zi mir derkont, tsu nokhn oysshprakh

00:02:31.380 --> 00:02:34.040
hot zi gezen az ikh bin nit keyn, Litviner.

00:02:34.401 --> 00:02:40.709
hot zi genumen shoyn zogn, "farhalt im! zey hobn okersht opgeshnitn, litvishe kinder di oyvern,

00:02:40.709 --> 00:02:41.685
di yidn.

00:02:42.484 --> 00:02:45.313
farhalt im; mir darfn shoyn avekfirn im in GESTAPO."

00:02:46.230 --> 00:02:50.645
meyle, ikh bin kam-kam ⟨aroys,⟩ ikh bin kam fun dortn aroys a lebediker fun dem magazin.

00:02:50.668 --> 00:02:54.239
zikh genumen dreyen dortn, mentshn iz geven ful, hob ikh zikh durkhgerisn un bin avek.

00:02:54.786 --> 00:02:56.957
gekumen aheym on broyt, on keyn zakh.

00:02:57.975 --> 00:03:00.348
nu, nokh dem hot zikh ongefangen,

00:03:00.355 --> 00:03:02.492
m'hot genumen khapn mentshn in shtot

00:03:02.768 --> 00:03:04.013
oyf arbet.

00:03:04.013 --> 00:03:05.794
m'hot genumen khapn mentshn,

00:03:05.794 --> 00:03:09.512
firn oyf di fortn tsum shi- dershosn tsu vern.

00:03:10.176 --> 00:03:13.120
mir hot men ongekhapt in shtot

00:03:13.399 --> 00:03:18.658
un m'hot mir glaykh otpravet oyf der arbet makhn a tsam arum geto.

00:03:18.597 --> 00:03:20.228
ver hot aykh ongekhapt?

00:03:20.710 --> 00:03:25.425
 Litviner, mit vayse...

00:03:25.363 --> 00:03:26.774
bender, ya?

00:03:26.022 --> 00:03:28.145
bender oyfn hant, ye, mit biksn.

00:03:28.145 --> 00:03:29.643
zey flegn arumgeyn,

00:03:29.818 --> 00:03:34.930
zey flegn arumgeyn iber di gasn un, un ver s'iz geven zey fardekhtikt az m'iz a yid,

00:03:34.930 --> 00:03:37.965
flegn zey glaykh onnemen un glaykh avekfirn dortn vu m'hot gedarft.

00:03:37.965 --> 00:03:39.640
zey hobn mir ongekhapt,

00:03:39.640 --> 00:03:44.710
avekgefirt mir dortn bay zey in a, in a politsey,...

00:03:43.858 --> 00:03:44.982
opteylung?

00:03:44.710 --> 00:03:45.540
opteylung.

00:03:45.715 --> 00:03:50.940
un fun dortn hot men a gantse grupe ⟨OTN-⟩ avekgetribn

00:03:50.946 --> 00:03:54.652
in Slabodke shteln a shtekhldikn tsam.

00:03:54.979 --> 00:03:56.930
do hob ikh opgearbet

00:03:57.072 --> 00:03:58.854
mistome bay a monat tsayt.

00:03:59.468 --> 00:04:02.077
un bay nakht fl-, flegt ir, zikh umkern...?

00:04:00.970 --> 00:04:02.482
oplozn aheym.

00:04:02.472 --> 00:04:05.588
un ir hot shoyn gemuzt oyf morgn, zikh meldn, ya?

00:04:05.070 --> 00:04:06.296
y- vi den?

00:04:06.370 --> 00:04:10.110
un vi hobn zey dos kontrolirt az ir, az ir vet zikh meldn?

00:04:09.610 --> 00:04:17.670
es flegn, s'iz geven spetsyele mentshn vos zey hobn gesh-, gevizn vi me darf dem tsam s-... s'iz geven, dray reyen iz geven der tsam, dray reyen shtekhldike drot...

00:04:17.862 --> 00:04:19.596
s'iz geven spetsyele mentshn

00:04:19.596 --> 00:04:24.090
vos zey hobn gevizn vi me darf stroyenen dem tsam, vu me darf shteln di s-...

00:04:22.160 --> 00:04:24.859
UNK dos zaynen geven yidn, tsu Litviner?

00:04:24.409 --> 00:04:25.545
Litviner.

00:04:25.303 --> 00:04:26.326
Litviner.

00:04:25.545 --> 00:04:29.280
vu me darf shteln di s- di, stolbes mit altseding.

00:04:28.780 --> 00:04:33.105
ober vi iz, vi hobn di Litviner kontrolirt az ir vet kumen oyf morgn oykh?

00:04:33.105 --> 00:04:35.844
vi zaynen zey geven zikher, tomer kumt ir nit oyf morgn?

00:04:35.631 --> 00:04:39.080
zey hobn gehat ⟨far- ge-⟩ farshribn alemen's, vu, v-...

00:04:38.230 --> 00:04:39.253
adresn?

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:41.801
adresn vu me lebt, di familyes mit altseding.

00:04:41.993 --> 00:04:43.559
un zey hobn glaykh gedrot:

00:04:43.559 --> 00:04:47.386
far nit kumen vert men glaykh dershosn. dos iz geven der ershter,...

00:04:48.979 --> 00:04:51.723
der ershter zeyer, ⟨, z- d-⟩ drot, ye, ⟨az⟩...?

00:04:50.818 --> 00:04:52.027
drot, ye.

00:04:51.865 --> 00:04:56.162
flegt, ⟨, z-,⟩ flegt ir a gan- zay- hot ir a gantsn monat opgearbet bayn shtekhl-drot.

00:04:55.290 --> 00:05:00.448
bay a monat tsayt hobn mir opgearbet. hobn gearbet etlekhe hundert man hobn gearbet bay dem tsam, zeyer fil.

00:05:00.775 --> 00:05:02.861
der tsam iz shoyn gevorn fartik.

00:05:03.002 --> 00:05:06.725
nu, dan hot men gegebn a bafel arayntraybn alemen in geto.

00:05:07.450 --> 00:05:12.130
 in geto hot men arayngetribn. keyn mashines hot men nit gelozt ⟨f-⟩ araynfirn.

00:05:12.130 --> 00:05:15.500
flegt men trogn oyf zikh peklekh mit,

00:05:15.500 --> 00:05:20.260
mit mebl. me flegt oyf, mit, mit vegener mit ferd firn.

00:05:20.260 --> 00:05:23.390
s'iz geven a strashne, geven zeyer,...

00:05:22.105 --> 00:05:23.213
shreklekhe.

00:05:23.390 --> 00:05:25.389
tsum kukn iz geven zeyer troyerik.

00:05:26.374 --> 00:05:29.000
azoy hot men undz tsuzamengetribn in geto,

00:05:29.057 --> 00:05:31.768
a finf un draysik toyznt yidn.

00:05:32.213 --> 00:05:35.548
ir perzenlekh, vi hot ir gekrogn a voynung in geto?

00:05:36.280 --> 00:05:39.801
in geto bin ikh geven tsuzamen b- mit mayn shvester.

00:05:39.368 --> 00:05:40.442
mit Tshernen?

00:05:40.465 --> 00:05:45.640
Tsherne. ⟨i- ⟩ in geto hot men undz arayngetribn in I-

00:05:46.405 --> 00:05:48.120
in avgust mistome.

00:05:49.273 --> 00:05:54.780
un in SENTYABR' iz ⟨, D-⟩ Tsherne's, Dore geborn gevorn.

00:05:54.780 --> 00:05:57.232
in a monat arum iz zi geborn gevorn.

00:05:58.639 --> 00:06:01.586
yo, ober vi hot ir in geto gekrogn vu tsu...?

00:06:01.153 --> 00:06:08.300
me hot farteylt. m'hot farteylt. s'iz glaykh geshafn a yidishe, in yidishn komitet hobn zey geshafn spetsyele g-

00:06:08.300 --> 00:06:12.254
azelkhe grupes vos hobn genumen farteyln alemen...

00:06:12.254 --> 00:06:14.901
azoy vi bay undz iz geven zeyer a groyse familye,

00:06:15.312 --> 00:06:16.591
hot men undz gegebn

00:06:16.591 --> 00:06:18.747
oyf VIENOŽINSKIO gas,

00:06:19.277 --> 00:06:20.604
dortn a barak,

00:06:21.370 --> 00:06:23.878
numer fir un tsvantsik, gedenk ikh vi haynt,

00:06:24.458 --> 00:06:26.679
dortn hot men undz gegebn tsvey tsimern.

00:06:27.050 --> 00:06:28.350
far vifl perzon?

00:06:30.516 --> 00:06:32.282
vifl perzon?

00:06:33.115 --> 00:06:36.771
mir hobn gemuzt zayn mistome a draytsn, fertsn man hobn mir gemuzt zayn.

00:06:37.013 --> 00:06:41.327
un, dos iz, ir zayt geven mit Tshernen, un nokh a shvester iz oykh geven mit aykh?

00:06:41.063 --> 00:06:44.282
Tsherne iz geven; Tsherne's man iz geven;

00:06:44.282 --> 00:06:48.768
 der man hot gehat dray shvester, a muter; ikh hob gehat a bruder;

00:06:49.045 --> 00:06:51.992
nokh dem iz Do- Dore geborn gevorn.

00:06:52.217 --> 00:06:57.290
azoy arum az s'iz geven, s'iz, me flegt poshet, eyner lebn di andere lign.

00:06:57.027 --> 00:07:00.244
un vu iz geven ayer tsveyte shvester, vos zi hot gelebt oykh in...?

00:06:59.473 --> 00:07:04.411
di tsveyte shvester hot gelebt oyf, dan hot zikh gerufn ŠEŠIOLIKT⟨A⟩ VASARIO gas.

00:07:03.793 --> 00:07:08.343
vos iz geven ir g- ir, mit ir iz farfloygn, bayn onheyb fun der milkhome?

00:07:07.776 --> 00:07:10.014
ir iz gelungen tsu antloyfn.

00:07:10.155 --> 00:07:11.600
zi mitn man

00:07:11.910 --> 00:07:15.886
iz, glaykh in zelbn tog, ⟨ir hot, iz⟩ gelungen tsu antloyfn

00:07:16.602 --> 00:07:18.233
in Rusland.

00:07:19.403 --> 00:07:22.670
un zi hot ge- un zi iz, geforn i- in,

00:07:23.082 --> 00:07:25.556
Uzbekistan, stantsye KARAKUL'.

00:07:25.866 --> 00:07:27.142
dortn hobn zey gelebt.

00:07:29.629 --> 00:07:35.394
iz oybe ir v- volt gegangen tsu di, di tsveyte shvester, volt ir efsher aleyn oykhet derlofn biz Rusland.

00:07:36.025 --> 00:07:39.650
s'iz geven dan aza min lage az m'hot nit gevust vu me geyt

00:07:39.650 --> 00:07:42.431
un, un vos m- un vos es vart yedn eynem.

00:07:42.589 --> 00:07:44.000
keyner hot nit gevust.

00:07:44.040 --> 00:07:45.310
keyner hot nit gevust.

00:07:45.373 --> 00:07:47.720
⟨tsu s'iz⟩ geven a mazl-zakh⟨, ⟩...

00:07:47.753 --> 00:07:54.345
az, betn dem voynung in yidishn komitet, zayt ir gegangen, tsu ayer shvester's man iz ge...?

00:07:53.220 --> 00:07:55.998
neyn. dos iz geven mayn shvoger.

00:07:55.498 --> 00:07:57.416
ayer shvoger hot dos geton, ye?

00:07:56.730 --> 00:07:59.728
der shvoger hot gehat bakantshaft in komitet,

00:08:00.223 --> 00:08:04.014
un er hot gezogt az di froy darf ge- ot-ot geborn.

00:08:04.257 --> 00:08:07.221
nu, un er hot gekrogn oto di o tsvey tsimern.

00:08:08.813 --> 00:08:13.540
iz, nokh dem, az ir hot shoyn oysgeboyt, dem, dem shtekhl-dr...

00:08:12.019 --> 00:08:15.600
m'hot keyn zakh nit geboyt; s'iz geven ersht oysgeboyt, s'iz geven fartik UNK

00:08:14.854 --> 00:08:17.666
ye, sh- neyn, az ir hot oysgeboyt dem shtekhl-drot,

00:08:17.807 --> 00:08:21.395
mit vos hot ir zikh farnumen di ershte teg in g- zayendik shoyn in geto?

00:08:21.840 --> 00:08:23.572
in geto zayendik,

00:08:25.097 --> 00:08:26.694
m'hot gezukht vos tsum esn.

00:08:28.759 --> 00:08:30.764
vos iz? me flegt nemen fun shtub

00:08:30.764 --> 00:08:36.420
a mantl, a rekl, a zeyger, a ringele... un mir hobn gelebt lebn, leb- lebn, h-

00:08:36.420 --> 00:08:38.624
hart bayn tsam iz geven undzer barak...

00:08:38.631 --> 00:08:41.040
un fun yene zayt flegn kumen Litviner

00:08:41.040 --> 00:08:49.360
un m'hot, m'hot, far a halbn lebl broyt flegt men avekgebn a goldenem zeyger, a ring, a, ⟨me darf nit ba- mi- a,⟩ a mentsh, ⟨az er iz⟩ hungerik,

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:52.918
iz darf er dos keyn zakh nit hobn; er darf nor opesn, mer darf er nit.

00:08:52.924 --> 00:08:55.668
ir flegt oykhet, baytn zakhn oyf...?

00:08:54.713 --> 00:08:56.910
ye, baytn, bay⟨tn⟩.

00:08:56.890 --> 00:09:00.850
un, ven hot men aykh shoyn ongehoybn shikn oyf arbet?

00:09:01.767 --> 00:09:03.580
oyf arbet...

00:09:04.045 --> 00:09:06.370
s'hot ⟨bay, ge- iz⟩ geven aza min...

00:09:06.370 --> 00:09:11.760
az der vos hot nit gearbet, hot men nit gegebn keyn KARTOCHKe tsum esn.

00:09:11.858 --> 00:09:14.923
azoy arum az ikh bin geven getsvungen tsu geyn arbetn.

00:09:15.486 --> 00:09:22.630
arbetn bin ikh avek, me flegt nemen oyfn erodrom flegt men nemen. di merste teyl mentshn flegn geyn oyfn erodrom; tog-teglekh,

00:09:22.630 --> 00:09:25.993
dray, fir toyznt mentshn flegt men nemen oyfn erodrom.

00:09:26.134 --> 00:09:30.718
nu, azoy vi ikh hob nit gehat ⟨in... s'-⟩ s'iz geven di yidishe kolone-firer,

00:09:31.045 --> 00:09:33.868
flegn zey⟨ere⟩ nemen, zey hobn gehat gute brigades.

00:09:33.868 --> 00:09:35.775
zey flegn geyn arbetn in shtot.

00:09:35.775 --> 00:09:39.830
dortn iz geven laykhtere arbet. dortn flegt men kenen oysbaytn oyf produktn.

00:09:39.830 --> 00:09:45.585
ikh hob keyn bakante nit gehat, bin ikh gegangen oyfn erodrom; ⟨ikh bin⟩ geven a, vi me zogt, a "eybiker erodromshtshik" bin ikh geven.

00:09:46.249 --> 00:09:48.790
nu, dortn vos UNK bavegn,

00:09:48.790 --> 00:09:54.080
kalt, hungerik. me flegt undz gebn tsvey hundert gram broyt in tog... di broyt iz geven

00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:55.811
mit a pilke gebakn...

00:09:56.965 --> 00:10:02.820
mit a, a halbn liter, fun, fun kapu- fun kroyt

00:10:02.820 --> 00:10:07.489
farshtunkene flegt men undz gebn. dos iz geven un- der gantser, gantsn tog ⟨iz dos⟩ geven...

00:10:07.275 --> 00:10:09.496
dos iz a halber liter zup mistome, ya?

00:10:08.743 --> 00:10:09.986
zup, ye.

00:10:10.110 --> 00:10:13.394
vu hot, v- vu flegt men dos ⟨aykh gebn⟩? oyf aer- oyfn aerodrom gufe?

00:10:12.372 --> 00:10:18.306
dort oyfn erodrom iz geven a kikh, un dort hot men oyf an ort gekokht, un dortn g- gegebn esn dortn un...

00:10:18.396 --> 00:10:22.254
un oyf, frishtik ⟨arum,⟩ flegt ir vos nit iz bakumen ⟨g-⟩ gevise ⟨greys⟩?

00:10:21.028 --> 00:10:27.333
keyn zakh nit. keyn, dos iz geven di norme: tsvey hundert gram broyt mit, ⟨, ha-⟩ mit dem halbn liter, ⟨I VSЁ⟩.

00:10:27.340 --> 00:10:29.949
un, un dokh, un nor oyfn aerodrom?

00:10:29.854 --> 00:10:31.653
nor oyfn erodrom, ye.

00:10:31.137 --> 00:10:33.949
un akhuts aerodrom, in geto flegt ir keyn zakh nisht bakumen?

00:10:33.567 --> 00:10:34.759
keyn zakh nit.

00:10:35.170 --> 00:10:40.547
ikh hob dortn opgearbet oyfn erodrom tsvey yor tsayt hob ikh opgearbet. arbet dortn iz geven zeyer shver.

00:10:40.620 --> 00:10:43.710
zumer-tsayt flegn mir mit kirkes hakn dortn.

00:10:43.710 --> 00:10:48.040
dortn iz geven berg, flegn zey, hobn zey gevelt oysglaykhn, flegt men darfn m-

00:10:48.040 --> 00:10:51.920
minirn, oyfraysn di berg, ⟨hobn mir, flegn mir⟩ oyshakn griber

00:10:51.920 --> 00:10:53.945
un darfn dortn minirn un...

00:10:54.407 --> 00:10:56.544
nu, s'iz dortn geven di arb-...

00:10:55.133 --> 00:10:57.439
ver hot dos minirt? ir hot dos minirt?

00:10:56.888 --> 00:11:01.016
neyn, dos iz geven di daytshn. nor mir hobn zey gedarft alts tsugreytn altsding.

00:11:01.495 --> 00:11:05.404
vinter-tsayt flegn mir reynikn dem...

00:11:06.270 --> 00:11:08.356
vu s'lozn zikh arunter di eroplanen.

00:11:07.823 --> 00:11:10.466
dem veg tsu ero- di veg far di aeroplanen.

00:11:09.730 --> 00:11:15.150
dem veg. s'iz dortn zeyer, geven zeyer fil arbet. s'flegt, un s'iz geven zeyer a shverer vinter

00:11:15.150 --> 00:11:16.654
in eyn un fertsiktn yor,

00:11:16.654 --> 00:11:18.920
zeyer a kalter. s'flegt dergreykhn biz

00:11:19.800 --> 00:11:23.430
ts- akht un tsvantsik, draysik grad UNK.

00:11:24.462 --> 00:11:26.315
nu, flegn mir onlodn

00:11:26.315 --> 00:11:28.607
tsvey mashines mit shney,

00:11:29.153 --> 00:11:34.414
un s'iz, ⟨di⟩ kelt iz geven groys, flegn mir zikh nokh dem oysmakhn fun di shney, flegn mir makhn azelkhe,

00:11:34.414 --> 00:11:36.060
 shtibelekh,

00:11:36.060 --> 00:11:41.837
un biz di mashine flegt avekforn un kumen tsurik, flegn mir ⟨shoyn⟩ UNK in di shtibelekh onvaremen fun di shney.

00:11:42.484 --> 00:11:44.570
azoy hobn mir gearbet oyfn erodrom.

00:11:46.045 --> 00:11:51.439
un ir hot nisht prubirt, baytn di arbet, di arbet? dos iz geven ummeglekh?

00:11:50.601 --> 00:11:52.260
s'iz geven ummeglekh,

00:11:52.260 --> 00:11:54.859
vayle s'iz geven zeyer fil privilegirte,

00:11:54.859 --> 00:11:57.778
vos hobn gehant, gehat bakantshaft groyse.

00:11:57.778 --> 00:12:03.230
zey hobn gekent ant- hobn gekent, zey- do iz geven zeyer fil daytshishe yidn, vos hobn gekent di daytshishe shprakh gut.

00:12:03.230 --> 00:12:06.710
nu, zey hobn geven, zaynen geven oyfn ershtn ort tsum krign arbet.

00:12:06.852 --> 00:12:08.162
besere arbet?

00:12:07.695 --> 00:12:11.780
ye, besere arbet, ⟨vayl zey hobn⟩ gekent di shprakh, hobn zey gekent mit di daytshn zikh tsuzamenreydn.

00:12:11.780 --> 00:12:14.759
flegt men zey glaykh nemen in di beste brigades flegt men zey nemen.

00:12:16.318 --> 00:12:19.906
nu, zayendik, oyfn, zayendik oyfn erodrom

00:12:20.200 --> 00:12:25.054
⟨hob ikh⟩ durkhgemakht in geto etlekhe aktsyes, hob ikh gezen az do iz troyerik.

00:12:25.077 --> 00:12:27.757
ikh bin geven oyf di ershte aktsye v⟨u zey hobn⟩ avekgefirt

00:12:27.757 --> 00:12:30.082
di tsen toyznt man oyfn nayntn fort.

00:12:29.667 --> 00:12:31.900
dos iz oyf di groyse aktsye, azoy gerufn?

00:12:30.932 --> 00:12:32.647
oyf di groyse aktsye.

00:12:32.097 --> 00:12:34.301
ir zayt durkhgegangen di sortirung?

00:12:33.497 --> 00:12:35.760
ikh bin durkhgegangen. ⟨ikh bin ge-⟩...

00:12:34.830 --> 00:12:36.714
tsuzamen mit di gantse mishpokhe?

00:12:36.230 --> 00:12:37.530
gantse mishpokhe.

00:12:37.530 --> 00:12:41.526
fun undzer, fun undzer, rey, mir zaynen ga- a gants⟨e rey⟩ zaynen mir gegangen.

00:12:41.526 --> 00:12:48.105
ikh hob nokh gefirt, Doren in a vegele; zi iz dan geven mistome, kh'veys, tsvey monat, mer hot zi nit gemuzt zayn, tsu dray monat.

00:12:48.870 --> 00:12:50.960
nu, ⟨iz es⟩ a mazl-zakh,

00:12:50.960 --> 00:12:58.490
iz di muter, dem sh-, dem, d- Tsherne's man's muter hot men aroysgerisn fun di hent un m'hot ir avekgefirt,

00:12:58.490 --> 00:12:59.633
di shlekhte zayt,

00:12:59.633 --> 00:13:01.638
un mir zaynen ale durkhgegangen.

00:13:03.214 --> 00:13:05.469
nu, nokh dem

00:13:05.492 --> 00:13:10.649
hob ikh gezen az do, s'kumen, alemen's otshered vet kumen oyf, tsu geyn oyfn nayntn fort.

00:13:10.774 --> 00:13:14.109
bashlosn az me darf fun geto loyfn, vayle do iz keyn ort nit.

00:13:14.318 --> 00:13:17.140
hob ikh genumen zukhn a kontakt

00:13:17.254 --> 00:13:21.331
mit vemen oyf tsu farbindn zikh in vald mit di partizaner.

00:13:21.287 --> 00:13:25.466
ir hot gevust dan az in geto arbet shoyn a untererdishe organizatsye?

00:13:24.561 --> 00:13:26.225
ikh hob gehert,

00:13:26.569 --> 00:13:32.060
ober fun vemen, s'iz geven zeyer, zeyer KONSPIRATIV iz geven; m'hot keyner nit gevust.

00:13:32.222 --> 00:13:35.844
DAZHE eyner fun tsveytn hot nit gevust az der iz⟨, nu, der un dos⟩.

00:13:36.812 --> 00:13:37.970
 nu,

00:13:40.103 --> 00:13:43.286
tsufelik hob ikh zikh getrofn mit eynem a bakantn.

00:13:43.782 --> 00:13:46.476
geheysn hot er Moyshe Milner.

00:13:50.076 --> 00:13:51.960
vi hot ir zikh mit im getrofn?

00:13:52.101 --> 00:13:53.816
kh'hob zikh mit im getrofn in geto.

00:13:54.058 --> 00:13:57.528
er iz oykh geven a shnayder; kh'hob im gekont fun frier⟨, fun⟩...

00:13:54.160 --> 00:13:54.829
un...

00:13:56.607 --> 00:13:58.693
fun far der milkhome hot ir im gekent?

00:13:57.805 --> 00:13:59.570
ye, fun shtot nokh.

00:13:59.796 --> 00:14:03.580
nu, gekumen tsu reyd... er iz mir zeyer gut ge- ba- beyde gut bakant...

00:14:03.863 --> 00:14:12.784
nu, zog ikh im, "do iz, do iz far undz keyn ort nit. me darf zen fun danen tsu loyfn. anit,..." zog ikh, "oyb umkumen, beser umkumen vi a held in vald."

00:14:13.954 --> 00:14:17.760
nu, er hot derhert azelkhe verter,

00:14:17.760 --> 00:14:21.372
un er iz shoyn geven ⟨in kont- k- SVYAZet⟩ mitn ⟨PODPOL'-⟩...

00:14:20.198 --> 00:14:23.077
farbundn, y- mitn untererd, ya?

00:14:22.257 --> 00:14:24.833
mitn untererd, m- mit di organizatsye.

00:14:25.125 --> 00:14:27.650
er hot kontik d⟨os glaykh zey⟩ ibergegebn,

00:14:27.943 --> 00:14:31.835
un mir hot men... s'iz avekgegangen umgefer a vokh tsayt,

00:14:32.753 --> 00:14:38.029
hot er mir getrofn. zogt er, "in di geto-varkshtatn voltstu veln arbetn?"

00:14:38.760 --> 00:14:40.003
zog ikh,

00:14:40.380 --> 00:14:44.900
"mitn, mitn grestn fargenign!" vayle s'iz fort in a vareme POMESHCHENIE;

00:14:44.900 --> 00:14:46.170
 in a, i-...

00:14:44.900 --> 00:14:47.461
ikh darf nit shteyn oyfn kelt un frirn.

00:14:47.468 --> 00:14:48.846
in a tsimer, ya.

00:14:47.805 --> 00:14:50.769
nu, m'hot mir glaykh aribergehoybn in di geto-varkshtatn.

00:14:50.826 --> 00:14:52.375
vos iz geven der tsil?

00:14:52.375 --> 00:14:56.695
m'hot gedarft neyen far di partizaner vos geyen aroys in vald kleyder

00:14:56.695 --> 00:14:59.033
gedarft neyen. azoy vi ikh bin a shnayder,

00:14:59.033 --> 00:15:04.522
nu, hot men mir dortn arayngehoybn un m'hot mir avek⟨ge- dortn⟩ un ikh hob zikh farn⟨umen dortn⟩ mit di arbet.

00:15:04.714 --> 00:15:06.620
vayle dortn in di geto-varkshtatn

00:15:06.620 --> 00:15:10.243
zaynen oykh geven mentshn fun di untererdishe⟨,⟩ organizatsye.

00:15:10.367 --> 00:15:16.267
vifl hot men shoyn aykh ge- vos hot ir gekrogn, broyt vifl, az ir hot shoyn gearbet ⟨in di⟩ geto-varshtatn?

00:15:14.367 --> 00:15:18.160
do iz shoyn geven, do iz shoyn geven a bisele laykhter do.

00:15:18.383 --> 00:15:21.930
do flegt men gebn shoyn merer,

00:15:21.930 --> 00:15:25.310
broyt merer. do flegt men,

00:15:25.310 --> 00:15:27.236
do iz geven,

00:15:27.276 --> 00:15:29.600
gertener iz do geven bayn taykh.

00:15:29.723 --> 00:15:35.061
flegn mir d⟨UNK⟩ di varkshtatn nit vayt fun di gertner, flegn mir kenen fray dortn aruntergeyn,

00:15:35.061 --> 00:15:38.020
onraysn mern, ugerkes, un

00:15:38.020 --> 00:15:41.749
s'iz geven, geven gor an ander lebn, vi me zogt, ⟨,⟩ UNK.

00:15:41.282 --> 00:15:43.604
un broyt iz shoyn oykhet geven, merer?

00:15:44.488 --> 00:15:48.127
nu, broyt iz, mayn shvoger, Tsherne's man,

00:15:48.370 --> 00:15:51.800
 iz geven a groyser rizikant.

00:15:52.639 --> 00:15:56.835
vos flegt er ton? er flegt trogn fun geto ney-mashines.

00:15:58.849 --> 00:16:04.125
durkhgeyn durkhn, durkhn toyer mit a ney-mashin, du host gekent dershosn vern oyf an ort.

00:16:04.730 --> 00:16:06.740
 er hot rizikirt.

00:16:07.219 --> 00:16:11.590
er flegt trogn ney-mashines un er hot derfun zeyer gut fardint in shtot.

00:16:11.775 --> 00:16:16.725
vayl in geto, a ney-mashin hot men avekgegebn zeyer, far kleyne gelt,

00:16:16.725 --> 00:16:19.636
un in shtot hot men opgenumen zeyer groyse gelt ⟨derfar⟩.

00:16:19.636 --> 00:16:25.269
nu, azoy vi er flegt f- gut fardinen, flegt men, flegt men, keyn produktn hot undz shoyn nit gefelt in shtub.

00:16:25.326 --> 00:16:29.505
un vi, un er fleg brengen broyt fun, far di fardinte gelt, ye, fun shtot?

00:16:28.684 --> 00:16:32.680
me flegt shoyn kenen in, me flegt shoyn kenen koyfn in geto gufe

00:16:32.680 --> 00:16:37.233
broyt un ale zakhn, vayl do iz geven, mentshn vos hobn zikh farnumen mit derayn.

00:16:37.594 --> 00:16:41.250
DAZHE tsum trinken, branfn iz oykh geven in...

00:16:41.256 --> 00:16:43.444
in geto a meglekhkeyt tsu bakumen?

00:16:42.184 --> 00:16:44.422
ye, ye, UNK ⟨nor hobn⟩ gelt.

00:16:45.863 --> 00:16:50.210
nu, di lage iz shoyn gevorn a sakh beser. ikh hob opgearbet in di varkshtatn

00:16:52.528 --> 00:16:55.222
umgefer a onderhalbn yor.

00:16:57.827 --> 00:16:59.238
un nokh dem,

00:17:00.780 --> 00:17:03.001
 iz gekumen mayn rey tsu geyn in vald.

00:17:03.447 --> 00:17:07.339
un, zayendik in di varshtatn, flegt ir far di,

00:17:07.445 --> 00:17:10.814
f-, zayt ir shoyn geven a mitglid fun der untererdisher organizatsye?

00:17:10.500 --> 00:17:11.911
ikh hob nit gevust.

00:17:12.593 --> 00:17:16.687
FAKTICHESKIY bin ikh shoyn geven a mitglid, ober ikh hob, mir hot men keyn zakh nit gezogt.

00:17:16.727 --> 00:17:21.160
m'hot mir gegebn a, vi me zogt dos, a arbet: "ot dos iz dayn arbet,

00:17:21.160 --> 00:17:24.247
un dos muzstu ⟨IS-⟩ makhn azoy un azoy."

00:17:24.185 --> 00:17:28.482
un ir hot nisht g- un ir hot gevust az ir shteyt in a rey tsu geyn in vald?

00:17:27.560 --> 00:17:29.210
keyn zakh nit.

00:17:29.670 --> 00:17:32.786
nor kh'hob, gehat dem tsil

00:17:32.792 --> 00:17:37.730
un ikh hob geklert, "efsher vet kumen mayn," ⟨vi me, me zogt, "mayn⟩, mayn rey."

00:17:37.365 --> 00:17:42.556
un me, u- un aykh hot men gezogt az s'iz do a meglekhkeyt, ir zay- shteyt in rey tsu geyn in val-...?

00:17:41.533 --> 00:17:43.015
keyn zakh nit.

00:17:43.015 --> 00:17:45.330
s'iz geven oyf azoy fil konspirativ

00:17:45.330 --> 00:17:47.850
az m'hot keyn zakh nit gevust,

00:17:47.850 --> 00:17:50.972
vayle ven, kholile-vekhas, me volt zikh dervust,

00:17:50.972 --> 00:17:52.969
volt men umgebrakht di gantse geto.

00:17:53.464 --> 00:17:57.654
un in geto, lemoshl, ir zayt shoyn geven, bashtimt tsu geyn in vald bay zey,

00:17:57.654 --> 00:18:00.394
hot men aykh nisht gelernt militerishe oysshulung?

00:17:59.573 --> 00:18:00.714
gelernt.

00:18:00.805 --> 00:18:04.730
in geto iz geven gevezene ofitsern fun litvishe armey.

00:18:04.730 --> 00:18:10.249
geven Padison iz geven, a gevezener kapitan, s'iz geven, Ratner,

00:18:11.453 --> 00:18:16.810
vos zey zaynen geven gute in- instruktorn oyf, oyf gever. m'hot undz gelernt,

00:18:16.810 --> 00:18:19.200
vayl ikh bin dokh geven nokh nit keyn gedinter,

00:18:19.200 --> 00:18:21.690
un geyn dortn in vald, vi me zogt, mit a,

00:18:21.690 --> 00:18:25.537
mit a biks iz di zelbe zakh vi mit a shtekn oyb me ken zikh mit im nit bageyn.

00:18:26.320 --> 00:18:30.499
iz, ven hot men aykh onge- ongen- ongehoybn tsu lernen dos?

00:18:30.083 --> 00:18:35.139
dos iz shoyn geven umgefer a tsvey, onderhalbn monat farn aroysgeyn fun geto.

00:18:34.757 --> 00:18:37.501
o, dan hot ir shoyn farshtanen, dan hot men...?

00:18:36.343 --> 00:18:39.510
ye. s'iz geven a spetsyeler bunker in geto,

00:18:39.510 --> 00:18:43.640
dortn geven gever. dortn flegt men bashtimen a tsayt, flegn mir kumen

00:18:43.640 --> 00:18:45.490
zalbe drit, zalbe firt,

00:18:45.490 --> 00:18:51.810
un me fleg zikh mit undz farnemen. mir hobn gedarft dem biks fanandernemen. m'hot gedarft visn ale detaln, ale teyln fun im.

00:18:51.810 --> 00:18:53.570
m'hot im gedarft tsu- tsuzamenshteln.

00:18:53.570 --> 00:18:56.020
m'hot gedarft visn vi im oystsushmirn,

00:18:56.020 --> 00:18:58.983
vi oystsureynikn dem STVOL. m⟨'hot v- ⟩...

00:18:58.551 --> 00:18:59.777
di lupe, ya?

00:18:59.327 --> 00:19:03.660
nu, nit nor a biks: a AVTOMAT, a biks, granatn iz geven.

00:19:03.660 --> 00:19:10.690
geven farsheydene, farsheydene minim gever iz geven, vos m'hot gedarft ⟨mit zey⟩ ale bageyn: mit mines, vi me darf zikh bageyn, ⟨un...⟩

00:19:09.705 --> 00:19:15.217
un ir flegt, oh, dan hot ir dem ershtn, farshtanen az ir, az ir k- zayt a kandid-...?

00:19:13.958 --> 00:19:16.483
dan hob ikh shoyn farshtanen az ikh bin shoyn...

00:19:16.253 --> 00:19:17.698
a kandidat tsu geyn...?

00:19:16.894 --> 00:19:17.715
ya.

00:19:18.565 --> 00:19:26.068
un, vi, zogt mir, vi zet, vi hot dos oysgezen, ir hot gevust fun faroys di date az ir vet avekgeyn in vald ot dem tog?

00:19:25.787 --> 00:19:30.320
dos hot men mir gemoldn mit a tog farn aroysgeyn. eyn...

00:19:29.162 --> 00:19:30.691
ver hot aykh dos gemoldn?

00:19:31.035 --> 00:19:34.740
mir hot gemoldn eyner vos ikh hob im DAZHE nit gekont.

00:19:34.740 --> 00:19:38.167
er iz tsugegangen tsu mir un gezogt az "morgn geystu aroys in vald."

00:19:37.853 --> 00:19:41.222
in, in varshtatn iz er gekumen tsu aykh, tsu oyfn gas tsugegangen?

00:19:40.941 --> 00:19:42.285
in varkshtatn.

00:19:41.920 --> 00:19:43.162
gekumen tsu aykh?

00:19:42.645 --> 00:19:44.613
ye, in varkshtat iz er gekumen

00:19:44.940 --> 00:19:50.283
un er UNK gezogt, "du geyst aroys morgn in vald." far mir iz shoyn geven ⟨on-⟩ oyfgeneyt a por shtivl.

00:19:49.834 --> 00:19:51.178
ir hot dos gevust?

00:19:50.948 --> 00:19:55.770
ye., a por shtivl, a kurtke hob ikh shoyn gehat oyfgeneyt, a vinterdike hitl.

00:19:55.791 --> 00:19:57.540
nu, V OBSHCHEM...

00:19:57.681 --> 00:20:00.037
un shisn hot ir shoyn oykh gekent dan?

00:19:59.183 --> 00:20:00.122
ye.

00:20:01.849 --> 00:20:03.159
zogt mir...

00:20:01.933 --> 00:20:05.600
a biks hob ikh shoyn gehat an eygenem, vayl... ikh hob f- durkhgelozn...

00:20:05.600 --> 00:20:11.613
beshas di, di ershte, di ershte frage iz geven, beshas me hot mir ge- beshas ikh hob gezogt dem Milnern,

00:20:11.974 --> 00:20:15.110
hot men, di ershte zakh hot men mir geheysn geyn klaybn gelt in geto

00:20:15.110 --> 00:20:16.591
tsum koyfn gever.

00:20:17.172 --> 00:20:20.709
zaynen mir gegangen, ikh bin geven, un eyner iz geven Noske Itsikson.

00:20:21.357 --> 00:20:26.211
mir beyde flegn geyn shtendik klaybn gelt. mir hobn ongeklibn zeyer a groyse sume gelt,

00:20:26.453 --> 00:20:32.066
un far di gelt hot men gekoyft far undz gever. hob ikh shoyn gehat, oyf mayn teyl iz shoyn geven a biks.

00:20:32.173 --> 00:20:35.154
un vi flegt ir klaybn dos gelt,...?

00:20:34.705 --> 00:20:44.064
nu, mir flegn arayngeyn bay, umgefer bay bakante, vayl zeyer fil hobn mir shoyn gevust, zayendik in geto tsvey, dray yor, ⟨hot men shoyn gekent, di⟩ shkheynim gekent ale.

00:20:44.155 --> 00:20:49.970
flegt men zogn, mir geyen klaybn far oreme mentshn, mir geyen klaybn far, der geyt oys fun hunger,

00:20:49.970 --> 00:20:54.645
der darf hobn oyf medikamentn, oyf dos. ⟨un⟩ me flegt undz gebn vifl eyner hot gekont.

00:20:55.107 --> 00:20:56.839
dos iz geven daytshishe gelt?

00:20:56.640 --> 00:20:58.525
dos iz ⟨geven⟩ daytshishe gelt, ye.

00:20:58.363 --> 00:21:00.804
un azoy hot ir zikh, farshaft a biks.

00:21:00.287 --> 00:21:02.525
mir hobn geshaft aza sume gelt,

00:21:02.599 --> 00:21:08.440
un ikh mitn Itsikson hobn mir beyde geshafn a sume gelt UNK geklekt oyf tsvey biksn far undz beyde.

00:21:07.830 --> 00:21:12.144
 un, ver hot aykh ayngekoyft di biksn, di organizatsye tsu, tsu ir aleyn hot zikh z⟨ey ayngekoy-⟩...?

00:21:11.222 --> 00:21:12.954
neyn, di organizatsye.

00:21:12.808 --> 00:21:15.370
di organizatsye hot dos ayngekoyft far aykh di biksn?

00:21:13.305 --> 00:21:15.320
⟨di organizatsye, ye⟩.

00:21:15.370 --> 00:21:18.641
un ir hot, aykh hot men gelernt, shisn pinktlekh?

00:21:19.153 --> 00:21:22.809
s'iz, ir hot gehat a meglekhkeyt in dem bunker tsu shisn fun ayer...?

00:21:21.870 --> 00:21:24.010
neyn, shisn hobn mir nit ge⟨UNK⟩t.

00:21:23.659 --> 00:21:24.786
shisn nit?

00:21:24.317 --> 00:21:27.044
neyn. nor, nor zikh bageyn mit gever.

00:21:24.786 --> 00:21:26.049
nor tsuzamensh-...

00:21:26.882 --> 00:21:29.002
un der etsem shisn, ⟨d⟩⟨UNK⟩...?

00:21:27.979 --> 00:21:31.970
vayle shisn, dos iz geven a, nit, nit umbadingt

00:21:31.970 --> 00:21:35.195
tsum shisn; m'hot gedarft mernit visn zikh tsu bageyn mitn biks.

00:21:35.269 --> 00:21:39.420
shisn ken yeder eyner. me darf mernit visn, vi im ontsulodn,

00:21:39.420 --> 00:21:42.232
vi dem, vi dem KOROBKe a kvetsh tsu gebn, altsding.

00:21:43.453 --> 00:21:47.193
m'hot undz, d- oykh gelernt mit, biksn...

00:21:48.760 --> 00:21:50.332
vi rufn zikh onet?

00:21:52.498 --> 00:21:55.749
shtelt zikh aveket oyfn STVOL...

00:21:55.992 --> 00:21:57.386
oyfn lupe, ya?

00:21:59.518 --> 00:22:03.258
vos me zet far a kilometer dem mentshn zeyer,...

00:22:02.623 --> 00:22:04.389
a snayperisher biks?

00:22:03.788 --> 00:22:07.140
a snayperisher biks. mir flegn zey rufn dortn andersh.

00:22:07.140 --> 00:22:09.047
dem biks hot men undz gelernt.

00:22:09.424 --> 00:22:11.741
nokh dem iz geven biksn bay undz,

00:22:11.741 --> 00:22:16.560
flegn zey onton oyfn, ⟨oybn oyfn⟩ STVOL mit tsvey REZINKes;

00:22:16.560 --> 00:22:19.914
me shist a mentshn, hert men afile nit ot do in tsimer.

00:22:19.296 --> 00:22:23.850
aha, dos, ⟨, z-⟩ me, me zol farshtiln, shtiln dem, dem, d-...

00:22:21.658 --> 00:22:23.491
ye. ye.

00:22:23.683 --> 00:22:26.010
nu, m⟨i⟩t far- farsheydene biksn.

00:22:26.010 --> 00:22:29.735
gever iz geven, gever iz geven in geto nit veynik.

00:22:30.079 --> 00:22:36.670
zeyer fil hobn gearbet in di, in di, fortn, vu ⟨s'iz geven⟩ skladn mit gever.

00:22:36.670 --> 00:22:39.320
flegn dortn geyn yidishe brigades,

00:22:39.320 --> 00:22:42.790
flegt men dortn spetsyel shikn fun di o mentshn,

00:22:42.790 --> 00:22:46.680
flegt men dortn fanandernemen a biks un teylvayz im arayntrogn in geto,

00:22:46.680 --> 00:22:48.770
un dortn flegt men im tsuzamenshteln.

00:22:48.270 --> 00:22:51.183
ir hot gevust ve- az in geto firt zikh aza arbet?

00:22:51.865 --> 00:22:55.318
ikh hob gevust. UNK letste tsayt hob ikh zikh dervust.

00:22:52.894 --> 00:22:53.833
vi...

00:22:55.138 --> 00:22:57.714
vi hot ir zikh dervust? me hot aykh dos dertseylt?

00:22:57.822 --> 00:23:01.039
nu, m⟨'iz, az, az⟩ me interesirt zikh, dervist men zikh.

00:23:02.361 --> 00:23:05.342
nu, m'hot eyn mol gekhapt eynem, Mek⟨e⟩.

00:23:06.360 --> 00:23:14.659
UNK bay im, er hot gevelt durkhkrikhn durkhn tsam mit a pistolet, hot men im gekhapt un me hot im oyfgehangen un me hot im ge- ⟨ikh bin DAZHE⟩ geven bayn

00:23:14.659 --> 00:23:17.130
moment ven me hot im oyfgehangen.

00:23:16.215 --> 00:23:17.879
ir zayt geven bay dem, ye?

00:23:17.130 --> 00:23:19.010
ya, UNK, bay dem moment.

00:23:18.679 --> 00:23:22.570
un dan zayt ir shoyn geven a mitglid fun untererdisher organizatsye, tsu nokh n-...?

00:23:21.328 --> 00:23:22.790
nokh nit.

00:23:22.570 --> 00:23:23.381
nokh nit.

00:23:22.790 --> 00:23:23.887
nokh nit.

00:23:24.518 --> 00:23:26.220
un zogt mir aza zakh:

00:23:26.220 --> 00:23:31.026
ir hot dertseylt ayer mishpokhe az ir zayt a mitglid fun der un- untererdisher organizats-...?

00:23:29.344 --> 00:23:32.831
dos iz geven sh- shtreng farbotn.

00:23:33.343 --> 00:23:35.463
ikh bin aroys fun geto,

00:23:35.487 --> 00:23:38.760
hot DAZHE mayn shvester nit gevust az ⟨ikh bin⟩ avek.

00:23:38.423 --> 00:23:41.522
un ir hot af- nit gev- nit gezogt az ir geyt avek in vald?

00:23:40.684 --> 00:23:41.538
neyn.

00:23:42.287 --> 00:23:44.947
hot di shvester gemeynt az ir zayt umgekumen efsher.

00:23:44.667 --> 00:23:47.091
nu, alts meglekh.

00:23:46.995 --> 00:23:48.946
ir hot keyn eyn vort nit gezogt ayer...?

00:23:48.042 --> 00:23:49.386
keyn eyn vort nit.

00:23:50.033 --> 00:23:54.630
s'iz geven sh- shtreng, sh-, vos es ken shoyn

00:23:54.630 --> 00:23:57.975
shtrenger nit zayn. azoy iz geven di organizatsye.

00:23:56.260 --> 00:23:56.979
un...

00:23:57.812 --> 00:23:59.881
un ir hot oysgehaltn di distsiplin?

00:23:59.061 --> 00:24:01.670
ya. oysgehaltn bizn letstn vort.

00:24:01.322 --> 00:24:04.660
 vos iz farfloygn mit aykh az,

00:24:04.967 --> 00:24:06.783
 az di,

00:24:09.675 --> 00:24:13.297
az di, heyst dos, az m'hot aykh gezogt...

00:24:18.248 --> 00:24:20.368
az m'hot aykh gezogt az,...

00:24:25.437 --> 00:24:30.392
az m'hot aykh gezogt az, az m'hot ⟨itst⟩ gezogt az me darf aykh firn,

00:24:30.702 --> 00:24:33.598
az me dar⟨kh⟩ ay- aykh fir- az ir fort shoyn in vald?

00:24:33.165 --> 00:24:34.003
ya.

00:24:33.958 --> 00:24:36.247
v-, vos iz geven no- nokh dem?

00:24:36.777 --> 00:24:40.348
beshas m'hot, shoyn bashtimt mayn tog ven tsu forn in vald,

00:24:40.793 --> 00:24:42.393
hobn mir zikh tsuzamengeklibn

00:24:42.393 --> 00:24:46.040
do vu s'iz geven, oyf VARNIŲ gas iz geven der yidisher komitet.

00:24:46.395 --> 00:24:53.561
lebn komitet iz geven dortn aza min... nu, aza min, SARAY az dan... ikh veys nit vi dos ontsurufn... dortn mentshn hobn nit gelebt.

00:24:53.702 --> 00:24:55.906
dortn hobn mir zikh ale tsuzamengeklibn

00:24:56.031 --> 00:24:57.510
bay draysik man.

00:24:57.347 --> 00:24:59.011
dos iz geven vifl a zeyger?

00:24:58.950 --> 00:25:03.490
dos iz shoyn geven a zeyger, nayn in ovnt.

00:25:03.270 --> 00:25:05.339
a. zayt ir shoyn geven nokh der arbet?

00:25:05.802 --> 00:25:07.950
⟨n-⟩ dem tog hob ikh shoyn nit gearbet.

00:25:07.776 --> 00:25:10.031
dem tog, vos hot ir geton dem tog?

00:25:08.490 --> 00:25:09.590
neyn.

00:25:09.680 --> 00:25:11.414
kh'hob zikh gegreyt.

00:25:11.151 --> 00:25:12.748
vu, bay zikh in shtub?

00:25:12.552 --> 00:25:13.474
neyn.

00:25:14.037 --> 00:25:15.144
bay vemenen?

00:25:15.370 --> 00:25:21.030
nu, do iz geven a spetsyeler ort iz geven dortn, vos me hot, dortn flegt men darfn kumen zikh tsugreytn.

00:25:21.030 --> 00:25:23.880
dortn hot men mir shoyn gegebn zakhn ontsuton zikh:

00:25:23.880 --> 00:25:26.400
shtivl mit a kurtke mit altseding.

00:25:26.777 --> 00:25:33.588
nu, un dan zaynen mir avek ale oyfn bashtimtn ort lebn, dortn lebn VARNIŲ toyer. dortn hobn mir gevart,

00:25:33.763 --> 00:25:35.782
un s'hot gedarft kumen a mashine,

00:25:36.480 --> 00:25:39.260
a daytshishe, gedekt mit a brezent,

00:25:39.973 --> 00:25:42.551
un mit di mashine hobn mir gedarft avekforn.

00:25:42.551 --> 00:25:44.456
ale hobn gehat mit zikh gever.

00:25:45.289 --> 00:25:47.763
ikh bin geforn als postn,

00:25:48.732 --> 00:25:54.449
vayl undzer, di mashine iz geforn als brigade vos fort in,

00:25:54.449 --> 00:25:57.214
in di rayon oyf a gantse vokh arbetn,

00:25:57.355 --> 00:26:01.393
vayl azoy flegt men nit lozn fun geto keyn zakh aroystrogn oyf der arbet,

00:26:01.393 --> 00:26:05.080
un di vos flegn forn oyf a gantse vokh in di velder arbetn,

00:26:05.080 --> 00:26:10.193
flegt men lozn mitnemen zakhn dortn, pasude, me ken oysbaytn oyf tsum esn. ye.

00:26:08.661 --> 00:26:09.836
gefes, y-...?

00:26:10.193 --> 00:26:13.025
mir zaynen geforn als aza brigade zaynen mir geforn.

00:26:12.846 --> 00:26:17.600
un di gever fl-, hot ir ari-, di mashine iz arayngeforn in geto, tsu ir zayt ar-...

00:26:16.320 --> 00:26:20.265
 neyn. zi iz geshtanen, fun yene zayt ⟨iz zi⟩ geshtanen.

00:26:17.600 --> 00:26:19.202
ir zayt aroys tsu di mashine?

00:26:20.389 --> 00:26:24.736
baym postn, der, der postn iz geshtanen bayn toyer. ⟨es hot⟩ gebrent elektrye.

00:26:24.945 --> 00:26:28.579
s'iz shoyn geven opgeredt mit di, mitn komitet,

00:26:28.579 --> 00:26:30.441
eyner, Vershvovski.

00:26:32.404 --> 00:26:34.288
vos iz mit im geven opgeredt?

00:26:34.277 --> 00:26:38.000
az, haynt darf aroysgeyn a grupe partizaner.

00:26:37.483 --> 00:26:39.147
er hot gevust vegn d⟨er,...⟩?

00:26:38.243 --> 00:26:39.958
er hot gevust altseding.

00:26:39.998 --> 00:26:41.544
Vershbovski, ya?

00:26:40.791 --> 00:26:45.130
Vershvovski. nu...

00:26:47.828 --> 00:26:50.100
s'iz gekumen tsu forn di mashine,

00:26:50.292 --> 00:26:54.301
hot men glaykh oysgeloshn di elektrye bayn toyer, iz gevorn fintster.

00:26:54.662 --> 00:26:58.217
s'iz geven mart monat, iz shoyn ⟨d- in⟩ di lange nekht.

00:26:58.881 --> 00:27:04.450
dem daytshn hot men gegebn eyer mit puter mit shnaps, hot er zikh a bisl opgerukt in a zayt,

00:27:04.450 --> 00:27:09.130
un m'hot im gezogt az di brigade fort in Yaneve, in Yanever, in vald arbetn.

00:27:08.652 --> 00:27:09.945
in Yaneve, ye?

00:27:09.377 --> 00:27:12.280
ye, in Yaneve, ya, Yanever vald arbetn.

00:27:14.372 --> 00:27:16.875
azoy zaynen mir avekge- aroysgeforn fun geto.

00:27:16.768 --> 00:27:17.909
un i⟨r⟩...

00:27:16.875 --> 00:27:22.617
ikh bin gezesn, ikh bin gezesn oyfn, der, di mashine iz geven UNK gedekt mit a brezent, zaynen ale geven ineveynik,

00:27:22.658 --> 00:27:25.183
un ikh bin gezesn ongeton in a daytshishe uniforme

00:27:25.628 --> 00:27:28.370
mitn biks oyfn vinkl fun,

00:27:28.370 --> 00:27:30.026
fun hintn fun mashine,

00:27:30.150 --> 00:27:32.236
vayl azoy iz geven bay di day-...

00:27:30.218 --> 00:27:36.590
un, un vu hot ir, arayngenumen dem daytshishn, biks in hant? az, oyf der mashine hot men aykh shoyn gegebn?

00:27:36.529 --> 00:27:41.822
oyf der mashine. ikh bin geshtanen, UNK geshtanen lebn, lebn zikh, ⟨hob ikh avek⟩geshtelt dem biks.

00:27:41.676 --> 00:27:45.011
e- e- ver hot aykh gegebn? eyner a mentsh hot aykh gegebn a biks?

00:27:43.785 --> 00:27:46.270
ye. ikh hob zey nokh nit gekont, ot di...

00:27:46.270 --> 00:27:52.891
nokh dem hob ikh d- shoyn genumen derkonen, in mashine forndik, hob ikh genumen derkonen zeyere, ver zey zaynen. ikh hob zey nit gekont keynem.

00:27:53.657 --> 00:27:57.930
nu, azoy zaynen mir aroysgeforn fun geto.

00:27:57.977 --> 00:28:00.623
aroys fun geto, arayn ale in mashine,

00:28:00.623 --> 00:28:02.764
un mir zaynen aribergeforn dem brik,

00:28:03.343 --> 00:28:07.235
un mir zaynen tsugeforn biz, GESTAPO,

00:28:07.292 --> 00:28:13.381
vinkl, KĘSTUČIO, VYTAUTO PROSPEKT, dortn a vinkl.

00:28:13.381 --> 00:28:14.997
dortn hobn mir zikh opgeshtelt.

00:28:15.190 --> 00:28:17.780
dos iz geven a zeyger elf in ovnt.

00:28:18.919 --> 00:28:20.651
elf in ovnt iz dos geven.

00:28:21.653 --> 00:28:25.170
ikh... dortn iz geven far undz ongegreyt

00:28:25.170 --> 00:28:31.390
a zak mit gever oyf TOTORIŲ gas. me zol nit darfn arayntrogn in geto un nokh dem vider aroysfirn,

00:28:31.390 --> 00:28:38.842
flegt men dortn, geven a maline, un dortn flegt men alts lozn ⟨un, nu,⟩ m'hot gevust, UNK farbayforn UNK dan mitnemen.

00:28:38.680 --> 00:28:40.364
ober ir hot dos nisht gevust alts?

00:28:40.384 --> 00:28:41.930
ikh hob keyn zakh nit gevust.

00:28:42.392 --> 00:28:50.587
ikh bin gezesn oyfn breg mashine, hob ikh gekukt in GESTAPO vi es geyen arum di ⟨GE-⟩ GESTAPO UNK fentster, gebrent di elektrye umetum.

00:28:50.779 --> 00:28:58.282
UNK ⟨nu, mir zaynen⟩ dortn geshtanen umgefer a tsvantsik minut un efsher DAZHE nokh merer, biz m'iz avek, biz m'hot UNK ⟨tsu trogn dem zak⟩, altseding.

00:28:58.710 --> 00:29:02.830
nu, mir zaynen geshtanen a halb sho punkt antkegn GESTAPO.
